{"tid":1724210,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"打蛇隨棍上 唔係休息 係升級","createTime":"2019-11-15T11:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:17:50.000Z","uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"02f888e42411413c5c286a04c2286d55d000b223","tid":1724210,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:49:41.000Z","msg":"由星期一被三罷進化到星期五已經全港停課，兩條幹線中斷，經濟活動減半<br />\n中午各區和你lunch人數絕不少數<br />\n武力升級 交通不便無令抗爭者割席<br />\n相反15號晚6點，政府對維持一星期既半三罷繼續表示強硬回應<br />\n<br />\n事已至此絕不是休息時間，反而係針對政府記者會作出示威一方既回應<br />\n即日宣布下星期開始三罷全面升級<br />\n各區和你lunch人士將會發動和你全民一早三罷<br />\n由一早開始就係上班地區集合 全面阻塞公共運輸系統包括機場高鐵<br />\n<br />\n死線係下星期五前要求政府回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">升級 &gt; 死線</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗爭係要一鼓作氣 一而再 再而三</span></span>"},{"pid":"a811cdf1c269dfe0be4fad9af25c08f3eaf7ec61","tid":1724210,"uid":84363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:50:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0548ae773c18e59dd9daef878cb235829a15c9e8","tid":1724210,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:52:02.000Z","msg":"無理由係三罷初見成果時就自斷雙臂"},{"pid":"0fed7b7b3c6b35b175be15fbb1cc83b8cab9b3a1","tid":1724210,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:53:54.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"eb3e5239475f266a99109512fedf8ed743cd5845","tid":1724210,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06adb51b7de0d79ce5c50a360f5d2b258144a83","tid":1724210,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:17:50.000Z","msg":"推"}]}